The University of Petra is awarded the Alemanni Accreditation Faculty ( ASIIN ) History : 30-07-2019 02 : 48 : 02 Entitlements : 1152 Ummah University : The Faculty of Accreditation has been awarded the Faculty of Alumni ( ASIIN ) Certificate of Accreditation for the Department of Chemistry at the Faculty of Arts and Sciences at the University of Petra , and is the first department of His Master &apos;s degree in Arab universities to receive this accreditation degree which is consistent with the Faculty of Alumaniology Program of the University of Petra , which is equivalent to the 6th level of the Master of Learning Staff ( EQF LL ) .